<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>MY GOD, I HAVE FOUND</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Pathien, Na vangsakna chu ka mui,
 Hinna, kipahna lungmuonnate chu.

[V2]
 Hallelujah! lopi Nang a!
 Hallelujah! Amen!
 Hallelujah! Lopi Nang a! ei hihhalh kit in!

[V3]
 2. A thisan luonna apatin ka mui,
 Ka kulhpi leh bitna, ka muonna Pathien.

[V4]
 3. Ka thihna ding mawh thing kross ah A puoi,
 Tu'n chu mi gilote le a suokcha tau.

[V5]
 4. Belam No pieksa ziekin pawm ka hi,
 Pathien Amah ngei in A lemguot ahi.

[V6]
 5. Zie khawvel ahin gimtheih thuok mah leng,
 Ka mun ding van ahi, Krista kawm achun.

[V7]
 6. Ziehi hun mu'ng ka, Amah lemguot chu,
 A lopina keile ei chanpih ina.

[V8]
 7. Hung kit pai intin, ei hung pui ina,
 A Lalchutphah kawmah ei chutsak ina.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>4</hymn_number>
</song>